# Icon System

## Primary Library: Phosphor Icons

```typescript
// ✅ Standard import for Client Components
import { Gear, User, Chat } from "@phosphor-icons/react"

// ✅ SSR-safe import for Server Components
import { Gear, User, Chat } from "@phosphor-icons/react/dist/ssr"
```

## Brand Icons

```typescript
// Provider brand icons (custom)
import { OpenAIIcon } from "@/components/icons/openai"
import { ClaudeIcon } from "@/components/icons/claude"
import { GeminiIcon } from "@/components/icons/gemini"
```

## Exception Icons (Lucide)

```typescript
// Fallback for icons not in Phosphor
import { SpecialIcon } from "@/lib/icons"
```

## Icon Props

```typescript
// ✅ Use size and weight props
<Gear size={24} weight="regular" />
<User size={20} weight="bold" />

// Available weights: thin, light, regular, bold, fill, duotone
```

## Migration Notes

- Primary: `@phosphor-icons/react`
- Brand icons: `@/components/icons/[provider]`
- Exceptions: `@/lib/icons` (Lucide fallback)
- See `components/icons/README.md` for full details
